        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324645" xml:id="d1e155081">Stephanus, Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e155083">Eduensis</placeName>
                        episcopus</persName>, notum fieri volo presentibus et futuris quod <persName key="d1e24066" xml:id="d1e155087">Osmundus</persName> et <persName key="d1e24072" xml:id="d1e155090">Odo frater ejus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e155092">Marmania</placeName>
                    </persName> dederunt in elemosinam perpetuam ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e155095">Fonteneti</orgName> laudantibus
                    sororibus suis <persName key="d1e24078" xml:id="d1e155098">Adelina</persName> et
                        <persName key="d1e24084" xml:id="d1e155102">Petronilla</persName>
                    <num>xx</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript" xml:space="preserve">ti </hi>solidos quos annuatim dabant
                    eis monachi <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e155109">Fonteneti</orgName>
                    in martio pro omnibus querelis quas tam pater eorum quam ipsi habuerant adversus
                    eamdem domum <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e155112">Fonteneti</orgName>. Calumpniati enim fuerant eis decimas in terris quas
                    excolebant in territorio <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e155115">Fanii</placeName>, partem etiam orti subtus abbatiam et pratum sub chimino
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e155118">Fanii</placeName> ubi
                    miles jacet,
                    et<hi rend="background(yellow)" xml:space="preserve"> leschariam</hi> desuper
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e155125">Fanium</placeName>, et
                    terram supra eamdem lescheriam ubi salices edificate erant, et omnes vineas quas
                    monachi tenebant in territorio <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e155128">Fanii</placeName>, vineam scilicet <persName key="d1e24091" xml:id="d1e155131">Rainaldi <addName>Esbrasati</addName>
                    </persName>, vineam <persName key="d1e24097" xml:id="d1e155136">Odonis <addName>
                            <foreign>Brandun</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, vineam <persName key="d1e24103" xml:id="d1e155142">Varnerii <addName>
                            <foreign>Viticot</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> et terram quam habebat ad censum pro duobus nummis in costa
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324489" xml:id="d1e155149">Morville</placeName>.
                    Quicquid in his omnibus juris habebant <persName key="d1e24109" xml:id="d1e155152">Osmundus</persName> et <persName key="d1e24115" xml:id="d1e155155">Odo</persName> ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e155158">Fonteneti</orgName> concesserunt ad censum <num>xx</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript">ti</hi> solidorum quos postea predicte ecclesie sicut
                    prediximus in elemosinam dederunt et mansum in quo grangia eorum erat quod
                    tenuerunt <persName key="d1e24121" xml:id="d1e155167">Andreas</persName> et
                        <persName key="d1e24128" xml:id="d1e155170">Felix</persName> et quicquid
                    habebant a rivo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325253" xml:id="d1e155173">
                        <foreign>Curtresum</foreign>
                    </placeName>
                    <hi rend="italic" xml:space="preserve"> </hi>usque ad finagium <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e155179">Marmanie</placeName> a chimino
                    sursum et quicquid habebant in <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325295" xml:id="d1e155182">Grenchessania</placeName> in bosco et in plano. Hoc totum
                    factum est laudantibus sororibus eorum et sciendum quod pro hac elemosina
                    habuerunt de beneficio ecclesie <num>xxx</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript">ta</hi> libras. Unde testes sunt monachi <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e155191">Fonteneti</orgName>
                    <persName key="d1e24134" xml:id="d1e155193">Willermus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324331" xml:id="d1e155195">
                            <foreign>Naille</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e24140" xml:id="d1e155199">Willermus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e155201">Curte Rabodi</placeName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e24146" xml:id="d1e155204">Hugo frater
                        ejus</persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e155207">Odo
                        archipresbiter <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e155209">Tullionis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e24152" xml:id="d1e155213">Umbertus capellanus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324350" xml:id="d1e155215">Raveriis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e24158" xml:id="d1e155218">Stephanus
                            <addName>Villanus</addName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e24165" xml:id="d1e155223">Petrus <addName>
                            <foreign>Allerez</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>. Hec omnia se fecisse, dedisse et laudasse coram me recognoverunt
                    duo supradicti fratres <persName key="d1e24171" xml:id="d1e155229">Osmundus</persName> et <persName key="d1e24177" xml:id="d1e155232">Odo</persName> et ut sigillo nostro confirmarem postulaverunt. Proinde ut
                    ista in posterum stabili firmitate conserventur cartam presentem sigilli nostri
                    munimine confirmamus et omnes qui de hiis ecclesiam <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e155235">Fonteneti</orgName> in aliquo vexare
                    aut dampnum aliquid ausi fuerint inferre donec resipiscant anathemate dampnamus,
                    amen. Actum anno incarnationis domini nostri Ihesu Christi millesimo centesimo
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">lxx° vii°</hi>.</p>
